getAssociatedObject

public final java.lang.Object getAssociatedObject()
Returns:
an object representing the Data associated to the plot: - A pie Piece if the plot is a PiePlot - A Double if the plot is a BarPlot - A Point if the plot is a Plot2D - A Bubble if the plot is a BubblePlot Before calling this method, you have to check if the Element Type is corresponding to what you are expecting.
